<script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function () {
        $('.language-button').on('click', function () {
            var language_code = $(this).data('language-code');
            document.cookie = "lang=" + language_code + "; path=/";
            location.href = "/";
        });

        var value = getCookie("lang");
        $('.language-button').each(function () {
            if ($(this).data('language-code') == value) {
                $(this).css({
                    padding: "2px",
                    borderBottom: "2px solid #ffeb3b"
                });
            }
        })

    });

    function getCookie(name) {
        const value = `; ${document.cookie}`;
        const parts = value.split(`; ${name}=`);
        if (parts.length === 2) return parts.pop().split(';').shift();
    }

</script>

</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function () {
        var days = $(".hidDays>input").val().split(",");
        var months = new Array("01", "02", "03", "04", "05", "06", "07", "08", "09", "10", "11", "12");

        setInterval(function () {
            var am_pm;
            var d = new Date();
            var s = d.getSeconds();
            var m = d.getMinutes();
            var h = d.getHours();
            var day = d.getDay();
            var date = d.getDate();
            var month = d.getMonth();
            var year = d.getFullYear();

            if (date < 10) { date = "0" + date }
            if (s < 10) { s = "0" + s }
            if (m < 10) { m = "0" + m }
            if (h > 12) { h -= 12; am_pm = "PM" } else { am_pm = "AM" }
            if (h < 10) { h = "0" + h }
            if ($(".UIClockSystem .clock").attr("type") == "1547")
                $(".UIClockSystem .clock").text(`${year} 年 ${months[month]} 月 ${date} 日，${days[day]}`); 
            else
                $(".UIClockSystem .clock").text(days[day] + ', ' + date + "/" + months[month] + '/' + year);
        }, 1000);
    });
</script>
